title: KISS Guitarist Ace Frehley Remembered By Bandmates, Rock Legends
description: Ace Frehley, the original lead guitarist for KISS, died after being taken off a ventilator following a nasty fall and a brain bleed ... and tributes are pouring in from tons of rockers, including his KISS bandmates Gene Simmons and Paul Stanley. In…
